Webcam Photographer

You can take photographs through your webcam with this application.

If you want to try out latest development version;
First, install PIL(python-imaging), PyQt4(python-qt4), python-opencv
Then, use these commands:
svn co http://kamera.googlecode.com/svn/trunk kamera
cd kamera
python setup.py build
python kamera/main.py

Kamera icon is taken from Tulliana 2.0 icon set
